      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, my left eye is looking really red and it's kinda painful too. there's a lot of gunk/discharge in it when i wake up. i've been staring at my laptop all day for work so i'm guessing it's just really bad dry eyes from screen time. do u think i can just get some lubricating eye drops from the pharmacy to clear it up?",
