      "content": "idk im just really busy with work right now and going to the clinic is such a hassle. if it's just some irritation from the screen, wouldn't the drops help soothe it anyway? like, can i just try the drops for a few days and if it doesn't get better i'll see someone? i just really want to avoid the doctor if i can help it.",
