    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay, i'll try the drops for a bit then. since it's pretty painful, should i just use a lot of them throughout the day to keep it hydrated? and i have some old antibiotic eye drops from a previous prescription in my cabinet, would it be okay to use those instead to make sure the infection is gone? i really want to just fix this myself so i can get back to work.",
